text: Ignacio Fernández may refer to: * Carlos Ignacio Fernández Lobbe (born 1974), Argentine rugby union player * Ignacio Allende Fernández aka Torbe (born 1969), Spanish porn actor, director, and businessman * Ignacio Fernández Esperón (1894–1968), Mexican composer * Ignacio Fernández Rodríguez (1980-), Spanish footballer * Ignacio Fernández Rouyet (born 1978), Argentina-born Italian rugby union player * Ignacio Fernández Sánchez (1922–2012), Spanish actor, director, and comedian * Ignacio Fernández Toxo (born 1952), Spanish activist, currently General Secretary of the Workers' Commissions Union (CCOO) * José Ignacio Fernández Palacios (1967-), Spanish former footballer * Ignacio Fernández (footballer) (born 1990), Argentine footballer
